			"editorData": {
				"HowToTrigger": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "- Load up GustavDev/BGO_Main_A\r\n- Use \"oe SAM_Crypt\" and \"SetGlobalOsirisFlag WYR_SentientAmulet_Knows_ShirraIsInCrypt\"\r\nOR\r\nUse \"oe SAM_Start\", talk to Sister Yannis in the Open Hand Temple after her discussion with Valeria, ask about Shirra Clarwen and then head down to the crypt.\r\n- Make sure you haven't read the plaque on Shirra's coffin or opened the tomb yet."
				},
